課程概述 Course Description
       本課程主要介紹射頻微波通訊系統電路相關原理、功能、發展歷程、架構、設計考量與實際應用，重點包含：無線通訊射頻系統簡介及需求設計、無線電波訊號功率傳輸、雜訊/非線性現象、射頻微波網路及傳輸線原理與分析、射頻微波被動電路設計/主動電路設計(低雜訊放大器、混頻器、功率放大器….等等)、射頻接收機及發射機系統等。CH1 Introduction to Wireless Communication Systems- CH2 Transmission Lines & RF PASSIVE COMPONENTS- CH3 Microwave Network Analysis- CH4 Microwave Passive Components: Power Dividers, Directional Couplers, & Hybrids- CH5 Impedance Matching & Tuning- CH6 RF/Microwave Filters- CH7 RF/Microwave Resonators- CH8 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: Amplifier- CH9 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: Mixer- CH10 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: Oscillator- CH11 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: VCO & Frequency Synthesizer- CH12 Wireless Communication Transmitter/Receiver RF Characteristics    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
射頻微波主動/被動積體電路及射頻通訊系統之一定深度的課程內容.. 

