備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
        無    

核心能力 Competence
■ 具電腦與通信工程相關領域之專業知識。
 To possess professional knowledge in the field of computer and communication engineering.
□ 策劃及執行專題研究之能力。
 The ability to plan and carry out a research project.
■ 撰寫專業論文之能力。
 To write a professional-quality dissertation.
□ 創新思考及獨立解決問題之能力。
 Innovative thinking and the ability to solve problems independently.
□ 跨領域人員協調整合之能力。
 Multidisciplinary coordination and integration capabilities.
□ 良好的國際觀以及實踐專業倫理與理解社會責任之能力。
 A solid international outlook and the ability to understand professional ethics and social responsibility.
□ 領導、管理及規劃之能力。
 Leadership, management and planning abilities.
□ 終身自我學習成長之能力。
 The ability to learn and develop throughout life.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       CH1 Introduction to Wireless Communication Systems- CH2 Transmission Lines & RF PASSIVE COMPONENTS- CH3 Microwave Network Analysis- CH4 Microwave Passive Components: Power Dividers, Directional Couplers, & Hybrids- CH5 Impedance Matching & Tuning- CH6 RF/Microwave Filters- CH7 RF/Microwave Resonators- CH8 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: Amplifier- CH9 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: Mixer- CH10 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: Oscillator- CH11 Active RF/Microwave Communication Circuits: VCO & Frequency Synthesizer- CH12 Wireless Communication Transmitter/Receiver RF Characteristics 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    射頻微波主動/被動積體電路及射頻通訊系統之一定深度的課程內容
     

